    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>障子、冲动、SHOJING <br>突破，跟随你的直觉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/a957f7da4558ba628b6afcde962b6498.poster.avif?t=1764689272\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/a957f7da4558ba628b6afcde962b6498.webm?t=1764689272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/a957f7da4558ba628b6afcde962b6498.mp4?t=1764689272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《SHOJING》是一款休闲游戏，您可以控制一只猫突破障子萤幕。 您不想以拆解现实世界中不该被破坏的障子屏为乐吗？请不要模仿好孩子或猫。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/441a29a9b60b25200da66d3d36ac9828.webp?t=1764689272\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/441a29a9b60b25200da66d3d36ac9828.poster.avif?t=1764689272\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需移动滑鼠并单击左键即可轻松操作。即使是平常不玩游戏的人和小孩也能轻松玩到。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/9454f74fdb6bd541ddbbf2c1dbd50f04.poster.avif?t=1764689272\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/9454f74fdb6bd541ddbbf2c1dbd50f04.webm?t=1764689272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/9454f74fdb6bd541ddbbf2c1dbd50f04.mp4?t=1764689272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >聲音</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猫咪随着BGM的节奏跳跃并打破障子萤幕。 连线连击会加快BGM和游戏速度，增加快感！ 让我们跟着节奏，打破障子！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >竞速破关</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作起来很简单，但如果你想完美地打破障子，你需要极其精确地使用它。 连接连击，避开障碍，争取高分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/0af88b1a32831facbeb642f45b9d43c5.poster.avif?t=1764689272\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/0af88b1a32831facbeb642f45b9d43c5.webm?t=1764689272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/0af88b1a32831facbeb642f45b9d43c5.mp4?t=1764689272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
